attributes.value: Level three: Taking it up another notch / The lyrics are hot, the beats are so fresh, you can't stop.

metadata.description: "CYDI", or "Can You Dig It?" by Makio135 is an homage to the history and culture of hip hop as seen through digital coding. This collab collection between Makio135, The Universal Hip Hop Museum and Iconic Moments is a new and completely innovative extension of hip hop, using the digital world to express the analog origins of the movement and the impact it has had. Can you dig it?
metadata.title: CYDI - can you dig it?
